          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Target consisted of Al, Cu, and Mylar foils. The",
                "target foils were 5 cm square and its composition:",
                "Foil Material Thickness (mg/cm2)",
                "1       Al         4.8",
                "2       Al        42.7",
                "3       Al         4.7",
                "4     Mylar       17.5",
                "5     Mylar       17.7",
                "6       Cu         9.3",
                "7       Cu       233.9",
                "8       Cu       234.4",
                "9       Cu         9.3",
                "10    Mylar       17.6",
                "11    Mylar       17.6",
                "Total            609.5"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Ge(Li) detector system."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " During the 497-min irradiation a nearly",
                "constant flux of approximately 6 x 10**7 particles",
                "per min passed through the target. After irradiation",
                "the target was flown to Brookhaven and gamma-ray",
                "assays were begun 14 hours after the end of",
                "bombardment. 24Na production in Al foil 2 served as",
                "the beam monitor. On the basis of the",
                "27Al(40Ar,X)24Na the total fluence was determined to",
                "be 2.9 x 10**10 40Ar ions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Standard errors assigned to the cross",
                "sections are based on the estimates of errors from",
                "counting statistics, resolution of gamma-ray spectra,",
                "etc., or on the agreement of multiple determinations",
                "whichever was larger. They do not, in general,",
                "include systematic effects such as the uncertainties",
                "in the monitor cross section (15 %) or gamma-ray",
                "abundances. However, where several gamma rays were",
                "assayed for one nuclide, the errors include",
                "contributions from uncertainties in both the",
                "efficiency and abundance."
              ]
            }
          ],
